OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1782229703
OL,3,CManchester United secures more than
OL,4,Chalf of the land needed for new stadium
OL,6,FManchester United FC has now bought
OL,7,Fmore than half of the land needed for
OL,8,Ftheir new 100,000-seater stadium.
OL,10,FThe ground, which will become the
OL,11,Fbiggest sporting arena in the UK, will
OL,12,Fbe a stone's throw from Old Trafford.
OL,14,FThe club said it will serve as a
OL,15,Fcatalyst for the regeneration of the
OL,16,Fsurrounding district.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
