PN,36602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1782229703
OL,3,CManchester United secures more than
OL,4,Chalf of the land needed for new stadium
OL,6,FCollette Roche, CEO, Manchester
OL,7,FUnited's New Stadium Development,
OL,8,Fsaid, "The land we've acquired gives
OL,9,Fus the stage to deliver a truly world-
OL,10,Fclass stadium that honours our past
OL,11,Fand is ready for our future."
OL,13,FThe news marks a major milestone in
OL,14,Fthe long-term vision to transform the
OL,15,FOld Trafford area.
OL,17,FFormer Mayor of Greater Manchester and
OL,18,Fnew Makerfield MP Andy Burnham has
OL,19,Fbeen involved in the stadium
OL,20,Fregeneration plans.
OL,26,@sD@]O]
