CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1782229703
OL,3,CManchester United secures more than
OL,4,Chalf of the land needed for new stadium
OL,6,FHe previously told the Manchester
OL,7,FEvening News, "We have a really clear
OL,8,Fprinciple here at the start of this
OL,9,Fjourney with the Mayoral Development
OL,10,FCorporation. Manchester United will be
OL,11,Fpaying for the stadium.
OL,13,F"There will not be a penny of public
OL,14,Fmoney going into that, but we have
OL,15,Fabsolutely a role to play in making
OL,16,Feverything around the stadium as good
OL,17,Fas it can be because of the economic
OL,18,Fbenefit that brings."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
