OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1782229703
OL,3,CManchester United secures more than
OL,4,Chalf of the land needed for new stadium
OL,6,FManchester United plans new 100,000-
OL,7,Fseat stadium and regeneration of Old
OL,8,FTrafford site >
OL,10,FThe club acquired the 25-acre site,
OL,11,Fabout 350-meters north-west of the
OL,12,Fcurrent stadium, from Indurent, a
OL,13,Fleading provider of industrial space
OL,14,Fand a Blackstone portfolio company.
OL,16,FUnited said it will engage directly
OL,17,Fwith businesses impacted by the plans
OL,18,Fto support them through the transition
OL,19,Fperiod.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
