PN,36605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1782229703
OL,3,CManchester United secures more than
OL,4,Chalf of the land needed for new stadium
OL,6,FThe club said it has also worked
OL,7,Fclosely with Trafford Council and the
OL,8,FOld Trafford Regeneration Mayoral
OL,9,FDevelopment Corporation (OTRMDC) to
OL,10,Ffit into the wider Old Trafford
OL,11,Fregeneration strategy and to ensure
OL,12,Ffans have the best possible experience
OL,13,Fthrough optimum connectivity.
OL,15,FThe 370 acre regeneration project is
OL,16,Fexpected to deliver around 15,000 new
OL,17,Fhomes, including affordable housing,
OL,18,Fcreate 48,000 new jobs locally and
OL,19,Fover 90,000 nationally, and add more
OL,20,Fthan #7 billion a year to the UK
OL,21,Feconomy.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
