OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1782229703
OL,3,CManchester United secures more than
OL,4,Chalf of the land needed for new stadium
OL,6,FUnited said the development will help
OL,7,Fto create one of the most "dynamic and
OL,8,Fglobally significant sporting and
OL,9,Fentertainment destinations in the
OL,10,Fworld."
OL,12,FMs Roche added, "Being able to build
OL,13,Fso close to Old Trafford allows us to
OL,14,Fpreserve the heritage, traditions and
OL,15,Frituals that are so important to our
OL,16,Ffans.
OL,26,@tD@QOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
