CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1782229703
OL,3,CManchester United secures more than
OL,4,Chalf of the land needed for new stadium
OL,6,F"We are committed to building a world-
OL,7,Fclass stadium with our supporters, not
OL,8,Fjust for them, with atmosphere,
OL,9,Faffordability and accessibility at the
OL,10,Fheart of our thinking. "
OL,12,FThe OTRMDC will publish its vision for
OL,13,Fthe Old Trafford Regeneration on
OL,14,FThursday 9 July, when further detail
OL,15,Fof the stadium site and formal
OL,16,Fconsultation period will also be
OL,17,Frevealed.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
